OL,3,COne of the British Isles' oldest
OL,4,Cdrummers dies aged 102
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News in 2022, he
OL,7,Fremembered how his father was so
OL,8,Funimpressed that he threw it out of
OL,9,Fthe window.
OL,11,FAlfred never gave up though, even
OL,12,Fafter getting a job in engineering,
OL,13,Fand performed in the UK and USA over
OL,14,Fmany decades.
OL,16,FPerhaps most notably, he played for
OL,17,FSir Winston Churchill during the
OL,18,FSecond World War.
